Coding styles:

- Use TypeScript
- Use semicolons
- Use tabs for indentation
- Use single quotes
- Always use tailwindcss
- Always format & lint the code
- Avoid repeating the same code
- Extract functions to separate files if they are/can be reused
- Always use `const` instead of `function` for the component function
- Use currency.js when dealing with money
